cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Ella — Claude Code AI Agent for Any Business"
message: "If you use this software or its architecture patterns, please cite it."
type: software
authors:
  - given-names: Daniel
    family-names: Gonell
    website: "https://danielgonell.com"
repository-code: "https://github.com/newmindsgroup/ella-claude-code-ai-agent"
url: "https://danielgonell.com"
abstract: >-
  Ella is an autonomous, single-tenant AI chief-of-staff agent built on
  Claude Code. It runs always-on on a small VPS, reachable via Telegram and a
  Mission Control dashboard, with a multi-tenant template that takes a fresh
  business from a blank server to a working agent in under an hour. Features a
  SQLite + vector memory layer, three-tier sub-agent delegation (Agent tool /
  domain swarms / OpenSwarm), proactive watchers, an observability stack, and a
  voice-capable chat surface synced across Telegram and web.
keywords:
